<title>USA: Viewlogic chairman Hanover to resign.</title>
<headline>Viewlogic chairman Hanover to resign.</headline>
<dateline>MARLBORO, Mass. 1997-01-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Viewlogic Systems Inc said on Thursday the chairman of the board, Alain Hanover, will step down as chairman of the board following the annual meeting on May 13.</p>
<p>Hanover has served as chairman and chief executive since the company was started in 1984. Earlier today the company said it named William Herman the new chief executive.</p>
